                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18220703-15-off74 t18220703-15-cd75"></join>, one gown, value 4 s., and two handkerchiefs, value 6 d.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t18220703-15-victim168" type="victimName">
                     Esther 
                     Goulbourn
